# Build-context excludes for `docker build` (both Dockerfile and Dockerfile.dev).
# NOTE: `.railwayignore` only governs Railway uploads; local/Pi builds need this.
# Do NOT add a bare `*.sql` line — migrations/*.sql must ship in the prod image.

.git
.claude/
.dev-ssh/
.venv

**/__pycache__
*.pyc
.pytest_cache
.ruff_cache
.ropeproject
htmlcov
.coverage

*.env
manifest.zip
manifest/
world_sql_content*
scratch/
kyber-*.sql

docs/
plans/
